<meta property="og:title" content="Class Of 2015 IIT Bombay "><meta property="og:type" content="article"><meta property="og:site_name" content="Google Docs"><meta property="og:url" content="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1XtipVHgj2nb-mQ6Gv1kulH2mepopUEQmF3lkyzNiExc/viewform?c=0&amp;w=1&amp;usp=embed_facebook"><meta property="og:image" content="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/6qDCcFnfrNIHOeX9QuZ5O23Sc4w4r_NSZ5dtKUnZDvEW59aW1fpQEjnK0HeqaLrs6EE=w1200-h630-p"><meta property="og:image:width" content="1200"><meta property="og:image:height" content="630"><meta property="og:description" content="You will be graduating in a few months.Even though you will be leaving IITB, IITB won’t be leaving you.In order to connect you to larger set of alumni, folks who graduated last year and all the way to 50 years back, IITBombay Alumni Association recommends you to complete this form. 

How does it work?
The process of collecting database ends with the Institute Valedictory Function, post which all your records are noted. Then no matter where you take up your job/higher studies, we arrange welcome parties for you through our already established alumni network which is spread around the world. Through this we connect you to seniors and super seniors. We will also send you timely invites and updates about any IITB reunions and events that might be happening around you.

In addition to this, there are several resources and advisory committees that are open to you, and a more in depth idea of how to use these resources will be shared in the function.

At the end of this form, you will be asked to put in your T-Shirt size and an option to be associated with the Give One Program of IITB, a fundraising initiative where young alumni pledge 1% of their future income toward supporting overall improvement and excellence at IIT Bombay.

If your place of posting/university for further studies is not decided yet, fill &#39;Undecided&#39; for both chapter and country and Please ensure to remain connected and get back to us with the developments.You may write at iitbaa.office@iitbombay.org so that we can update records.This will help us to connect you to to your chapter !"><meta name="twitter:card" content="player"><meta name="twitter:title" content="Class Of 2015 IIT Bombay "><meta name="twitter:url" content="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1XtipVHgj2nb-mQ6Gv1kulH2mepopUEQmF3lkyzNiExc/viewform?c=0&amp;w=1&amp;usp=embed_twitter"><meta name="twitter:image" content="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/6qDCcFnfrNIHOeX9QuZ5O23Sc4w4r_NSZ5dtKUnZDvEW59aW1fpQEjnK0HeqaLrs6EE=w435-h251-p-b1-c0x00999999"><meta name="twitter:player:width" content="435"><meta name="twitter:player:height" content="251"><meta name="twitter:player" content="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1XtipVHgj2nb-mQ6Gv1kulH2mepopUEQmF3lkyzNiExc/viewform?c=0&amp;w=1&amp;embedded=true&amp;usp=embed_twitter"><meta name="twitter:description" content="You will be graduating in a few months.Even though you will be leaving IITB, IITB won’t be leaving you.In order to connect you to larger set of alumni, folks who graduated last year and all the way to 50 years back, IITBombay Alumni Association recommends you to complete this form. 

